<%- include('partials/header') %>

<section class="page-heading animate-in">
  <div>
    <p class="eyebrow">Emergency Readiness</p>
    <h1>Preparedness Guide</h1>
    <p>Essential checklists and steps to keep you and your family safe during disasters.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="details-layout animate-in">
  <div class="content-panel">
    <div class="guidance-panel">
      <h2>🎒 Essential Emergency Kit</h2>
      <p>Keep these items in an easy-to-carry bag (Go-Bag) near your exit.</p>
      <div class="guidance-grid">
        <div class="mini-panel">
          <h3>Basic Needs</h3>
          <ul class="guidance-list">
            <li>Water (3 liters per person per day)</li>
            <li>Non-perishable food (biscuits, energy bars, canned food)</li>
            <li>First-aid kit and essential medicines</li>
            <li>Battery-powered or hand-crank radio</li>
            <li>Flashlight with extra batteries</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="mini-panel">
          <h3>Important Items</h3>
          <ul class="guidance-list">
            <li>Copies of ID cards, insurance, and bank details</li>
            <li>Cash in small denominations</li>
            <li>Local maps and emergency contact list</li>
            <li>Power bank and charging cables</li>
            <li>Multi-purpose tool (Swiss knife)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="guidance-panel" style="margin-top: 40px;">
      <h2>🌊 Flood Safety</h2>
      <ul class="guidance-list">
        <li><strong>Before:</strong> Identify higher ground and the quickest route to get there.</li>
        <li><strong>During:</strong> Avoid walking or driving through flood waters. Turn off utilities at the main switch.</li>
        <li><strong>After:</strong> Only return home when officials say it is safe. Watch out for snakes and downed power lines.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="guidance-panel" style="margin-top: 30px;">
      <h2>🌀 Cyclone/Storm Safety</h2>
      <ul class="guidance-list">
        <li><strong>Before:</strong> Board up glass windows or put storm shutters. Trim dead branches from trees.</li>
        <li><strong>During:</strong> Stay indoors. Move to an inner room, away from windows.</li>
        <li><strong>After:</strong> Check for gas leaks. Keep clear of damaged buildings.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="side-panel">
    <div class="side-section" style="border-top: 0; padding-top: 0;">
      <h3>Emergency Helpline</h3>
      <div class="helpline-list">
        <div class="helpline-item">
          <strong>National Emergency</strong>
          <span class="badge high">112</span>
        </div>
        <div class="helpline-item">
          <strong>Police</strong>
          <span class="badge high">100</span>
        </div>
        <div class="helpline-item">
          <strong>Fire</strong>
          <span class="badge high">101</span>
        </div>
        <div class="helpline-item">
          <strong>Ambulance</strong>
          <span class="badge high">102</span>
        </div>
        <div class="helpline-item">
          <strong>Disaster Management</strong>
          <span class="badge high">108</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="side-section">
      <h3>Quick Action</h3>
      <p class="muted">Ensure your profile is updated with your latest location for accurate alerts.</p>
      <a href="/auth/profile" class="btn btn-secondary" style="width: 100%;">Update Profile</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
